data.description: Ball Ground downtown is the place for family friendly, fun loving  gatherings.  Come and find out how easy it is  to be in restaurants, park or Botanical Garden in this sweet spot. Schools, tennis courts or downtown concerts you can leave the car behind and enjoy a walk with your 4 legged friend. Ranch home offers just under 2 acres with privacy plus convenience. FULL  basement ready for your ideas or your STUFF!! Home office or weekend getaway this location can become your forever home by adding your personal touch. Full home generator, full home dehumidifier, almost new roof and lots of privacy!!!  Home has recently been used for filming retro cooking show and has the look of going back to Grandma's house. Country cooking or country living you can do it all right in the middle of Ball Ground. Property is minutes away from 50 acre walking park and truly accessible to everything a family would enjoy. Creek or mountain view you can find it all as easily as walking out your door and heading to Calvin Farmer Park. Make plans to visit Ball Ground and find out how easy it can be to leave the hustle and bustle behind.
